  "description": "A coastal scene depicting a bird standing on wet sand near the breaking waves of the ocean. The bird, appearing to be a shorebird, has a speckled brown and white plumage and is gazing slightly downward. Another bird is captured mid-flight, wings outstretched, above the first bird. The foreground consists of dark, wet sand reflecting the sky. The ocean waves range in color from turquoise to white as they roll towards the shore, creating a foamy texture. The overall composition emphasizes the interaction between the birds and the marine environment.",
